 :title "Test Generation for Phase Files",
 :task/intent
 "Generate unit and integration tests that verify:\n               - Phase lifecycle (enter, leave, error handlers)\n               - Agent invocation and result handling\n               - Metrics tracking and aggregation into execution metrics\n               - Error recovery and retry logic with budget enforcement\n               - Context propagation and phase state transitions\n               - Registry integration via multimethods",
