  "Test files should be: test/ai/miniforge/phase/*_test.clj"
  "Include integration tests for full phase execution cycles"],
 :task/description
 "Create comprehensive tests for the verify, review, and release phase\n               interceptors that were autonomously generated by miniforge during the\n               meta-meta loop bootstrap session.",
 :task/code-artifact
 #:code{:id #uuid "59761a35-f97e-4a40-87a5-9191460c1806",
        :language "clojure",
